OL,3,CFrom ministers to NHS doctors: Who is
OL,4,Cto blame for the infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FEarlier this year, a seven-year public
OL,8,Finquiry published its final report,
OL,9,Fwhich it said will provide a measure
OL,10,Fof justice to the thousands of people
OL,11,Faffected in what has been called the
OL,12,F"biggest treatment disaster in NHS
OL,13,Fhistory".
OL,15,FAccording to the report, the patients
OL,16,Fhad been failed "not once, but
OL,17,Frepeatedly" by doctors, the
OL,18,Fgovernment, the NHS, and others.
