OL,4,Cto blame for the infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FOn Friday the government announced
OL,8,Fvictims of the scandal will receive
OL,9,Fcompensation for life.
OL,11,FThe government did not say how much
OL,12,Fthey expect the scheme to cost but
OL,13,Fawards for those at the top end are
OL,14,Flikely to exceed #2.5 million.
OL,16,FITV News outlines who exactly was
OL,17,Fresponsible for the disaster, and
OL,18,Fwhether or not they will face
OL,19,Fconsequences.
OL,21,FNHS and doctors
