OL,3,CFrom ministers to NHS doctors: Who is
OL,4,Cto blame for the infected blood
OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FSome of the worst mistakes of the
OL,8,Fscandal were made at Lord Mayor
OL,9,FTreloar College, in Alton, Hampshire,
OL,10,Fbetween the 1970s and 1980s.
OL,12,FSeveral of the male pupils who
OL,13,Fattended the boarding school at the
OL,14,Ftime were given treatment for
OL,15,Fhaemophilia at an on-site NHS centre
OL,16,Fwhile receiving their education.
