OL,5,Cscandal?
OL,7,FIt was later found that many pupils
OL,8,Fwith the condition had been treated
OL,9,Fwith plasma blood products which were
OL,10,Finfected with Hepatitis C and HIV.
OL,11,FMore than half of the students treated
OL,12,Fare now dead.
OL,14,FSchool administrators were not blamed
OL,15,Fin the report, but NHS clinicians who
OL,16,Ftreated boarding school pupils on the
OL,17,Fgrounds were.
